$ System.Threading.ExecutionContext (class)

`System.Threading.ExecutionContext` manages the execution context for the *current thread*.

The class behaves differently on → Microsoft/dot-net/implementations/Framework and → Microsoft/dot-net/implementations/Core.

sa:
  The → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/automatic[automatic] PowerShell variable → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/automatic/executionContext[`$executionContext`] is not related to this class.
